78
00:09:24.564 --> 00:09:28.902
So. JSS is not incompetent.

79
00:09:29.528 --> 00:09:30.862
he's just that great?

80
00:09:32.155 --> 00:09:33.240
It's true.

81
00:09:33.991 --> 00:09:36.618
He was wrongfully discharged
from the unit.

82
00:09:36.868 --> 00:09:38.203
Then worked as an elite

83
