fighter at a PMC called Blackstone.

84
00:09:41.498 --> 00:09:43.792
Blackstone? Elite?

85
00:09:44.209 --> 00:09:45.585
-By PMC. you mean...
-Yes.

86
00:09:46.211 --> 00:09:49.298
It's a global booming war agency.

87
00:09:49.715 --> 00:09:51.800
And he was a high-ranking soldier

88
00:09:51.883 --> 00:09:53.302
